Description:
Subnautica is a role-playing game from the creators of Natural Selection 2, in which the authors promised to combine cinematography, an open world and the development of "big" RPGs. Subnautica is a sandbox game with the open world created by Unknown Worlds Entertainment. The main feature of the game - all the action takes place in the alien ocean, where your spacecraft fell on the plot. Only one person survived: a player. He has only a life-saving capsule, and everything necessary for life and its protection will have to be extracted in the vast underwater world.
